-- Alstom CEO sees positive cash flow in 2014-15
-- By Natalie Huet
-- Tue Jan 21, 2014 04:38AM EST
-- None



PARIS, Jan 21 (Reuters) - Alstom <ALSO.PA> expects to generate positive free cash flow in the next fiscal year but will not make this a firm target, Chief Executive Patrick Kron told analysts on Tuesday after the company cut its guidance for the second time in nine months.

